About addon
===========

This directory contain addon software of tools for extmail project,
please read this document carefully and follow the instructions

Addon detail
============

MailGraph_ext
-------------

A RRDtool frontend for Postfix/Sendmail Statistics, originally written
by David Schweikert <dws@ee.ethz.ch>, now we develop a individial
queue monitor programe to generate queue graph.

Furthermore, we rewrite the web frontend and integrate into ExtMan.
Please read README.ext in the source directory for detail.

cleanup.sql
-----------

A sql script to destroy extmail MySQL data, use it as your own risk, it
will delete all data and your accounts will be lost!!

upgrade_a.b.c_to_x.y.z.sql
----------------------------
A series sql script to update extman SQL structure.

font.ttf
-----------

True Type Font (TTF) for captcha capability, this font is useful for
generating rotating captcha string in png/jpeg format using GD module.

The default font.ttf is Courier New (bold), you can upload your prefer
ttf font and like them as font.ttf
